1
00:00:00,510 --> 00:00:03,610
(Episode 139)

2
00:00:04,380 --> 00:00:06,010
He may be the majority shareholder,

3
00:00:06,280 --> 00:00:07,910
but he's a lawyer
with no hotel experience.

4
00:00:08,180 --> 00:00:10,220
Appointing someone like him
as an inside director...

5
00:00:10,650 --> 00:00:13,450
is a move that will drive our hotel
into the ground.

6
00:00:13,720 --> 00:00:15,150
This is a gamble. A huge gamble.

7
00:00:15,690 --> 00:00:19,220
As a shareholder,
I vehemently oppose the motion...

8
00:00:19,460 --> 00:00:20,860
to appoint Lawyer Kang Baek Ho
as the director.

9
00:00:21,230 --> 00:00:22,990
- That's right.
- Yes, he's right.

10
00:00:22,990 --> 00:00:24,800
Is this hotel some mom-and-pop shop?

11
00:00:28,800 --> 00:00:31,040
The foundation of management
is transparency.

12
00:00:33,140 --> 00:00:36,710
On the screen is the slush fund ledger...

13
00:00:36,710 --> 00:00:38,410
created by the arrested
former CEO Chae Hwa Young...

14
00:00:38,410 --> 00:00:39,540
and Manager Lee Kang Hyuk.

15
00:00:40,110 --> 00:00:41,880
Next to it...

16
00:00:42,380 --> 00:00:44,480
is how Executive Director Choi
and Managing Director Park,

17
00:00:44,550 --> 00:00:46,050
who just questioned my management skills,

18
00:00:46,250 --> 00:00:49,520
used a paper company
to assist with that slush fund...

19
00:00:49,520 --> 00:00:51,120
and took kickbacks.

20
00:00:51,960 --> 00:00:54,230
That's fabricated.

21
00:00:54,360 --> 00:00:56,430
The Prosecutor's Office will determine
whether it's fabricated or not.

22
00:00:57,260 --> 00:00:58,660
I am stripping all executives...

23
00:00:58,930 --> 00:01:00,900
who were complicit in Chae Hwa Young's
embezzlement and malpractice...

24
00:01:01,130 --> 00:01:03,070
of their positions,

25
00:01:03,400 --> 00:01:04,570
and I will hold them accountable...

26
00:01:04,570 --> 00:01:05,770
to the fullest extent
of civil and criminal law.

27
00:01:06,400 --> 00:01:07,970
Cutting out the corruption...

28
00:01:08,510 --> 00:01:12,340
will be the first demonstration
of my management.

29
00:01:45,040 --> 00:01:48,010
My judgment was clouded,

30
00:01:48,650 --> 00:01:53,280
and I allowed venomous snakes
to thrive in this hotel.

31
00:01:54,550 --> 00:01:55,590
But now...

32
00:01:56,690 --> 00:02:01,290
I intend to entrust this hotel
to the majority shareholder, Choi Ha Joon,

33
00:02:02,330 --> 00:02:04,360
no, Kang Baek Ho.

34
00:02:05,560 --> 00:02:07,900
Today, on the motion
to appoint Choi Ha Joon,

35
00:02:08,300 --> 00:02:12,370
no, Kang Baek Ho, as the new CEO,

36
00:02:12,770 --> 00:02:17,910
I will vote in favor
with all my shares and voting rights.

37
00:02:19,480 --> 00:02:20,750
So if any of you oppose this,

38
00:02:21,680 --> 00:02:26,280
you are free to leave
this company right now.

39
00:02:27,820 --> 00:02:33,890
As of today, I, Ma Dae Chang,
will step down from active management.

40
00:02:34,560 --> 00:02:37,400
I will only maintain my position
as Chairman of the board.

41
00:02:38,530 --> 00:02:42,900
At today's board meeting, I will appoint
majority shareholder Kang Baek Ho...

42
00:02:43,640 --> 00:02:46,640
as the new CEO of our Dream Hotel.

43
00:02:47,740 --> 00:02:50,170
The appointment is official.

44
00:02:53,750 --> 00:02:55,910
I will rebuild Dream Hotel.

45
00:03:21,810 --> 00:03:24,910
Darn it. Do you even have any idea
who I am to lock me in here?

46
00:03:25,580 --> 00:03:27,950
I'm Chae Hwa Young, CEO of Dream Hotel.

47
00:03:28,210 --> 00:03:30,150
What kind of stunt
do you think you're pulling?

48
00:03:30,580 --> 00:03:32,850
Get the chief of police in here now!

49
00:03:33,120 --> 00:03:35,490
Just wait until I get out.
You're all fired.

50
00:03:35,820 --> 00:03:37,490
Open the door. Open it, right now!

51
00:03:38,320 --> 00:03:40,690
Chae Hwa Young, you are a suspect,
so quiet down.

52
00:03:40,690 --> 00:03:41,730
What's your name?

53
00:03:42,160 --> 00:03:45,100
How dare you yell at me?
Do you have a death wish?

54
00:03:45,900 --> 00:03:47,170
You're unbelievable.

55
00:03:47,170 --> 00:03:48,430
- Wait!
- Get in!

56
00:03:49,730 --> 00:03:51,740
You found the brooch thief,
so you should know.

57
00:03:52,140 --> 00:03:54,270
I was just being blackmailed
by Chae Hwa Young.

58
00:03:54,770 --> 00:03:56,570
- Get in.
- Darn it.

59
00:04:02,880 --> 00:04:05,380
They say you meet your enemies
on a narrow bridge.

60
00:04:05,520 --> 00:04:06,920
And here we are.

61
00:04:07,190 --> 00:04:08,190
Jin Hong Ju.

62
00:04:08,720 --> 00:04:12,560
How dare you lie like that?
You were being blackmailed by me?

63
00:04:13,690 --> 00:04:14,990
Seriously, that's ridiculous.

64
00:04:15,990 --> 00:04:18,600
You chose to do it. You did.

65
00:04:19,000 --> 00:04:21,130
You did because you wanted Kang Baek Ho
for yourself.

66
00:04:22,370 --> 00:04:23,840
Chae Hwa Young!

67
00:04:24,300 --> 00:04:26,340
I'm ruined because of you.

68
00:04:26,870 --> 00:04:28,740
Do you have any idea
how much I've held back?

69
00:04:28,740 --> 00:04:31,410
Because of you,
I've been branded with a scarlet letter.

70
00:04:31,480 --> 00:04:33,540
Hey, Jin Hong Ju, let go of me.
That hurts!

71
00:04:33,540 --> 00:04:35,650
I might have been too scared of you
to do anything before,

72
00:04:35,710 --> 00:04:37,250
but I'm not afraid of you anymore.

73
00:04:37,250 --> 00:04:40,250
You're a pathetic weakling,
and you dare mess with me?

74
00:04:40,450 --> 00:04:42,950
What? You're about to get a beating
from me today.

75
00:04:43,220 --> 00:04:45,160
I'll make you pay for what you did
to my mother too!

76
00:04:54,300 --> 00:04:55,730
- Let go.
- Come with me.

77
00:04:55,900 --> 00:04:58,000
Wait a minute. Seriously.

78
00:04:58,400 --> 00:05:02,040
- Hey. Chae Hwa Young.
- Hey. You...

79
00:05:02,140 --> 00:05:03,740
Let go of me.

80
00:05:03,740 --> 00:05:06,010
That Jin Hong Ju. It hurts.

81
00:05:06,140 --> 00:05:07,980
I won't let you get away with this,
Jin Hong Ju.

82
00:05:08,110 --> 00:05:09,680
That hurts.

83
00:05:10,350 --> 00:05:11,780
That brat is so strong.

84
00:05:17,120 --> 00:05:18,120
Chairman.

85
00:05:18,890 --> 00:05:19,890
Chairman.

86
00:05:20,890 --> 00:05:23,730
Please, you have to help my Hong Ju.

87
00:05:24,760 --> 00:05:26,000
Hong Ju...

88
00:05:26,360 --> 00:05:29,530
couldn't defy Chae Hwa Young's threats.

89
00:05:30,500 --> 00:05:32,500
It's not because she's a bad person...

90
00:05:32,740 --> 00:05:35,740
that she cooperated
with Chae Hwa Young's plans.

91
00:05:36,140 --> 00:05:38,780
If she condoned and helped a plan
to harm my father,

92
00:05:39,040 --> 00:05:40,140
she must be punished.

93
00:05:41,450 --> 00:05:45,480
Suk Hee.
Please spare my Hong Ju, just this once.

94
00:05:46,320 --> 00:05:47,420
After all,

95
00:05:47,720 --> 00:05:50,320
I was your stepmother
at one point, wasn't I?

96
00:05:50,390 --> 00:05:51,890
Stepmother, my foot.

97
00:05:53,090 --> 00:05:54,690
I guess I meant nothing.

98
00:05:57,500 --> 00:05:58,730
Chairman.

99
00:05:59,960 --> 00:06:03,400
This stupid mouth.

100
00:06:04,340 --> 00:06:05,440
Yeom San Wol.

101
00:06:05,800 --> 00:06:08,710
As for Jin Hong Ju,
even if she turned herself in,

102
00:06:08,870 --> 00:06:10,510
she'll receive the punishment
she deserves.

103
00:06:11,180 --> 00:06:15,180
And in the past,
you were complicit in my kidnapping.

104
00:06:15,480 --> 00:06:17,550
You'll have to be punished
for that as well.

105
00:06:26,860 --> 00:06:30,090
Geum Soon. You won't pretend
you don't know me, will you?

106
00:06:30,290 --> 00:06:31,960
We were in the same boat, weren't we?

107
00:06:32,260 --> 00:06:36,500
You and I were two of a kind,
weren't we, Geum Soon?

108
00:06:36,570 --> 00:06:39,270
What do you think I can do?
Gosh, get off of me.

109
00:06:39,340 --> 00:06:41,640
- I have to cook.
- Geum Soon...

110
00:06:44,040 --> 00:06:46,640
My Hong Ju. What am I going to do?

111
00:06:47,910 --> 00:06:50,720
(CEO Kang Baek Ho)

112
00:06:56,250 --> 00:06:57,260
Baek Ho.

113
00:07:03,590 --> 00:07:06,660
An arrest warrant was issued
for Chae Hwa Young today.

114
00:07:07,330 --> 00:07:08,470
She's being sent
to the Prosecutor's Office...

115
00:07:08,530 --> 00:07:09,670
and then transferred
to a detention center.

116
00:07:11,770 --> 00:07:13,870
So, she's finally been
officially arrested.

117
00:07:14,310 --> 00:07:17,680
Now all that's left is for her to face
the judgment of the law.

118
00:07:30,620 --> 00:07:33,760
(Take this medicine,
and leave the rest to me.)

119
00:07:33,760 --> 00:07:36,360
Take this medicine,
and leave the rest to me.

120
00:07:48,640 --> 00:07:49,710
My head hurts.

121
00:07:51,210 --> 00:07:52,240
My head...

122
00:07:58,120 --> 00:07:59,120
Chae Hwa Young.

123
00:08:00,480 --> 00:08:02,620
Chae Hwa Young, snap out of it.

124
00:08:03,120 --> 00:08:04,760
Chae Hwa Young, open your eyes.

125
00:08:04,860 --> 00:08:06,120
We have a situation.

126
00:08:06,120 --> 00:08:07,690
It's the detainee Chae Hwa Young,
awaiting transfer.

127
00:08:07,830 --> 00:08:09,630
She had a sudden seizure,
and she's unconscious.

128
00:08:09,630 --> 00:08:11,700
- Chae Hwa Young.
- Chae Hwa Young.

129
00:08:14,700 --> 00:08:16,530
Before this patient collapsed,

130
00:08:16,870 --> 00:08:18,600
did she have a high fever
or any signs of vomiting?

131
00:08:18,670 --> 00:08:19,900
I don't know about a fever,

132
00:08:19,900 --> 00:08:22,070
but she seems to have hit her head
during a fight.

133
00:08:22,140 --> 00:08:23,340
It looks like her arm was bitten, too.

134
00:08:23,470 --> 00:08:26,640
But would that cause her to suddenly foam
at the mouth and have a seizure?

135
00:08:27,610 --> 00:08:30,280
It could be shock from a brain injury,

136
00:08:30,720 --> 00:08:33,150
but foaming at the mouth
and seizing suggests...

137
00:08:33,150 --> 00:08:34,520
an acute infection or complication.

138
00:08:35,290 --> 00:08:37,990
I'll administer first aid on the way.
Please, get in.

139
00:08:38,090 --> 00:08:39,090
Okay.

140
00:09:01,310 --> 00:09:02,550
Not bad, Lee Kang Hyuk.

141
00:09:03,010 --> 00:09:04,920
I didn't think you could orchestrate
something like this.

142
00:09:06,120 --> 00:09:08,050
We have nowhere else to go now.

143
00:09:08,890 --> 00:09:10,390
If we get caught, it's really over.

144
00:09:11,090 --> 00:09:12,260
We can't get caught.

145
00:09:13,020 --> 00:09:14,960
Oh Jang Mi, that clingy little brat.

146
00:09:15,990 --> 00:09:20,300
But Lee Kang Hyuk, you betrayed me.

147
00:09:20,900 --> 00:09:22,470
What happened to the wrench?

148
00:09:22,730 --> 00:09:25,100
That was my insurance policy.

149
00:09:25,740 --> 00:09:27,540
In case you decided to run off
with Kang Nam Bong.

150
00:09:28,970 --> 00:09:29,970
I'm sorry.

151
00:09:30,410 --> 00:09:32,310
So, do you have any money?

152
00:09:32,640 --> 00:09:33,640
No.

153
00:09:34,310 --> 00:09:35,850
Jun Ho didn't bring anything either.

154
00:09:35,910 --> 00:09:37,110
Hey.

155
00:09:37,110 --> 00:09:39,120
How are we supposed to flee the country
without any money?

156
00:09:40,020 --> 00:09:43,220
We'll be stuck on the run
until we're eventually caught.

157
00:09:43,920 --> 00:09:46,660
Rather than get caught, I'd rather die.

158
00:09:47,890 --> 00:09:48,960
I'm Chae Hwa Young.

159
00:09:49,630 --> 00:09:51,600
I wasn't meant to live like this.

160
00:09:51,730 --> 00:09:52,760
I know, Hwa Young.

161
00:09:53,800 --> 00:09:56,670
- You've always been a shining star to me.
- Shut up.

162
00:09:57,600 --> 00:10:00,140
What are you going to do?
I said, what are you going to do?

163
00:10:01,040 --> 00:10:04,380
Gosh, having everyone gather together
for a meal like this...

164
00:10:04,480 --> 00:10:06,510
feels like a proper life.

165
00:10:08,650 --> 00:10:12,820
Grandfather, after we eat,
I'll sing a song for you.

166
00:10:12,880 --> 00:10:16,050
Okay, my dear Bo Ra. Yes.

167
00:10:16,650 --> 00:10:18,090
Let him enjoy his meal first.

168
00:10:18,320 --> 00:10:20,320
And that's the right way
to speak formally, Bo Ra.

169
00:10:20,760 --> 00:10:24,130
- Yes, please enjoy your meal.
- Oh my.

170
00:10:27,870 --> 00:10:30,800
- I just need to take this call.
- Oh, sure.

171
00:10:31,600 --> 00:10:33,570
- Yes, let's eat.
- Yes.

172
00:10:34,310 --> 00:10:35,310
Yes, Detective.

173
00:10:35,940 --> 00:10:37,170
What did you say?

174
00:10:37,380 --> 00:10:38,710
Chae Hwa Young escaped?

175
00:10:39,840 --> 00:10:40,850
Yes, I understand.

176
00:10:42,150 --> 00:10:43,280
What did you say, Baek Ho?

177
00:10:43,850 --> 00:10:47,520
- Chae Hwa Young has escaped?
- No way.

178
00:10:48,220 --> 00:10:49,820
That wretched woman.

179
00:10:49,890 --> 00:10:52,060
That vicious woman escaped?

180
00:10:52,190 --> 00:10:53,620
Lee Kang Hyuk must have broken her out.

181
00:10:54,790 --> 00:10:55,990
Unbelievable. Seriously.

182
00:10:56,490 --> 00:10:59,800
- Wait, then it'll be on the news.
- It won't be on the news.

183
00:11:00,100 --> 00:11:01,470
If they announce that
Chae Hwa Young escaped...

184
00:11:01,530 --> 00:11:02,530
right after they finally caught her,

185
00:11:02,870 --> 00:11:04,440
the entire police department involved
will be crucified.

186
00:11:05,540 --> 00:11:08,610
Mom, Grandfather, please be careful.

187
00:11:09,240 --> 00:11:11,780
Chae Hwa Young is fuming.
There's no telling what she'll do.

188
00:11:11,840 --> 00:11:13,880
Okay, you be careful too.

189
00:11:14,710 --> 00:11:17,780
I'm relieved that
Baek Ho is with you, though.

190
00:11:24,220 --> 00:11:25,390
You're going to the US?

191
00:11:26,220 --> 00:11:27,220
Yes.

192
00:11:27,560 --> 00:11:29,590
I'm going to focus solely
on my main job as a chef now.

193
00:11:30,360 --> 00:11:32,500
Good, that's the right choice.

194
00:11:33,260 --> 00:11:35,430
But, Jun Ho,

195
00:11:35,830 --> 00:11:38,840
you can still make it
to Baek Ho's wedding, right?

196
00:11:40,240 --> 00:11:41,240
Of course.

197
00:11:42,040 --> 00:11:44,980
It's my only brother's wedding.
Of course I have to be there.

198
00:11:45,980 --> 00:11:48,380
I'd like to get a gift
for my sister-in-law.

199
00:11:48,780 --> 00:11:49,910
What do you think would be good?

200
00:11:51,650 --> 00:11:52,820
Don't worry about it too much.

201
00:11:53,320 --> 00:11:55,290
I understand everything.

202
00:11:55,350 --> 00:11:56,420
Actually,

203
00:11:56,950 --> 00:12:00,220
the whole world knows
what my birth parents...

204
00:12:00,220 --> 00:12:01,660
did to Jang Mi's family.

205
00:12:02,660 --> 00:12:04,300
For me to just be there...

206
00:12:05,330 --> 00:12:06,700
is honestly a bit shameful.

207
00:12:07,930 --> 00:12:09,430
And I feel so sorry to Jang Mi.

208
00:12:10,800 --> 00:12:12,570
(Complementary Colors)

209
00:12:13,070 --> 00:12:14,710
Complementary colors, you see,

210
00:12:15,370 --> 00:12:17,240
are red and green.

211
00:12:18,780 --> 00:12:22,480
If you wear them together,
it's incredibly tacky, you know?

212
00:12:22,610 --> 00:12:24,080
It must be because you're a professor,

213
00:12:24,420 --> 00:12:26,520
but the way you explain things
makes it so easy to understand.

214
00:12:28,620 --> 00:12:31,620
So how are we supposed to dress?

215
00:12:36,690 --> 00:12:37,700
Baek Ho.

216
00:12:39,030 --> 00:12:40,030
What?

217
00:12:40,760 --> 00:12:41,800
She escaped?

218
00:12:42,600 --> 00:12:43,600
Escaped?

219
00:12:43,970 --> 00:12:45,770
(Digital Forensics Lab)

220
00:12:45,870 --> 00:12:48,140
Lee Kang Hyuk just can't
let go of Chae Hwa Young.

221
00:12:48,740 --> 00:12:49,910
What a relentless man.

222
00:12:50,070 --> 00:12:51,610
If only we had thrown Lee Kang Hyuk
in jail too,

223
00:12:51,610 --> 00:12:54,010
we wouldn't have this mess.
It's such a shame.

224
00:12:54,510 --> 00:12:55,950
Has Jun Ho heard from them?

225
00:12:56,280 --> 00:12:59,650
No. Honestly, I'd be anxious
even if they did contact him.

226
00:13:00,120 --> 00:13:01,690
But the fact that they haven't
makes me even more anxious.

227
00:13:01,750 --> 00:13:03,120
I'm afraid they might have
fled the country.

228
00:13:04,190 --> 00:13:05,390
Would they have that kind of money?

229
00:13:06,190 --> 00:13:08,690
Don't worry,
they'll be caught soon enough.

230
00:13:09,190 --> 00:13:11,560
I'm going to talk with Detective Kim
a bit more before I leave.

231
00:13:11,800 --> 00:13:13,930
I'll stop by the office
and then head straight home.

232
00:13:14,700 --> 00:13:15,700
Be careful.

233
00:13:30,080 --> 00:13:33,750
Excuse me, miss. I'm sorry,
but can you take a look at this?

234
00:13:33,850 --> 00:13:35,050
Yes?

235
00:13:35,590 --> 00:13:36,590
What's the problem?

236
00:13:36,650 --> 00:13:40,390
It suddenly won't start.
Who am I supposed to call for this?

237
00:13:42,390 --> 00:13:44,360
- I don't know anything about car repairs.
- Goodness.

238
00:14:06,850 --> 00:14:08,590
Alright, Baek Ho.

239
00:14:09,450 --> 00:14:13,090
Jang Mi? Oh, she's not here yet.

240
00:14:16,530 --> 00:14:18,800
Jang Mi isn't answering?

241
00:14:30,470 --> 00:14:31,780
What in the world happened?

242
00:14:32,140 --> 00:14:36,510
- How could Jang Mi get kidnapped?
- I'm sorry, Father. I was wrong.

243
00:14:36,950 --> 00:14:39,220
I thought Chae Hwa Young
would go after Kang Jun Ho.

244
00:14:39,350 --> 00:14:41,020
What are you people even doing?

245
00:14:41,090 --> 00:14:43,450
How could this happen so soon
after Chae Hwa Young escaped?

246
00:14:43,650 --> 00:14:46,190
If a single hair on my daughter's head
is harmed, you'll all pay.

247
00:14:46,660 --> 00:14:47,890
I'm sorry, Chairman Martin.

248
00:14:48,330 --> 00:14:50,930
Our top priority is
Ms. Oh Jang Mi's safety...

249
00:14:50,930 --> 00:14:51,960
in this investigation.

250
00:14:52,430 --> 00:14:54,100
We're gathering all the CCTV footage
of highway entrances...

251
00:14:54,100 --> 00:14:55,130
within a five-kilometer radius
of the hotel...

252
00:14:55,530 --> 00:14:57,030
and from the national roads.

253
00:14:57,270 --> 00:14:59,970
As soon as we analyze it,
we plan to block off her escape routes.

254
00:15:00,170 --> 00:15:03,370
Chae Hwa Young's funds were cut off,
so she went after Jang Mi.

255
00:15:03,770 --> 00:15:05,080
She's definitely going to demand money.

256
00:15:05,440 --> 00:15:08,010
Those bastards. When they get caught,
I will make them pay.

257
00:15:14,420 --> 00:15:17,590
Jun Ho. Chae Hwa Young's side
will definitely call you.

258
00:15:17,790 --> 00:15:20,690
They're going to tell you to bring them
the money you got from Jang Mi's family.

259
00:15:21,430 --> 00:15:22,730
They still consider themselves parents,

260
00:15:23,190 --> 00:15:24,960
so they wouldn't want to cut ties
with you completely.

261
00:15:32,740 --> 00:15:33,800
No, this is...

262
00:15:35,210 --> 00:15:37,780
Oh my gosh,
look what they've done to Jang Mi.

263
00:15:39,880 --> 00:15:40,880
Jang Mi.

264
00:15:44,580 --> 00:15:45,580
Wait.

265
00:15:45,950 --> 00:15:49,890
Record it. And answer calmly.
You must not get emotional.

266
00:15:50,250 --> 00:15:52,290
Otherwise, they might hang up, okay?

267
00:15:52,960 --> 00:15:53,960
Okay.

268
00:15:55,890 --> 00:15:56,990
Jun Ho, it's me.

269
00:15:57,360 --> 00:15:59,900
- It's your dad.
- What is all this?

270
00:16:00,330 --> 00:16:01,930
You commit another crime?

271
00:16:02,270 --> 00:16:05,840
I'm sorry. We don't have time. So...

272
00:16:07,640 --> 00:16:08,840
Jun Ho, it's Mom.

273
00:16:09,840 --> 00:16:10,840
You...

274
00:16:11,510 --> 00:16:13,640
really stabbed us in the back, didn't you?

275
00:16:14,010 --> 00:16:15,950
Stop this now and let Jang Mi go.

276
00:16:16,850 --> 00:16:18,850
If you keep this up,
you'll only be adding to your crimes.

277
00:16:18,920 --> 00:16:20,380
I have nothing to lose now.

278
00:16:20,450 --> 00:16:24,020
If I go to prison now,
do you think I'll ever get out?

279
00:16:25,460 --> 00:16:26,720
Let's cut to the chase.

280
00:16:27,020 --> 00:16:28,460
I need money to leave the country.

281
00:16:29,130 --> 00:16:31,830
I'm calling because I decided to trust you
one last time as my son.

282
00:16:32,830 --> 00:16:33,930
Tell her you'll give her the money.

283
00:16:36,730 --> 00:16:37,940
How much do you need?

284
00:16:38,200 --> 00:16:39,400
Now listen carefully.

285
00:16:39,870 --> 00:16:41,810
Make sure you tell Jung Suk Hee
and Chairman Ma...

286
00:16:42,470 --> 00:16:44,040
that if they want to save Oh Jang Mi,

287
00:16:44,340 --> 00:16:45,880
they have to prepare
three million dollars.

288
00:16:47,140 --> 00:16:50,610
They kidnapped me just to get money
for their escape?

289
00:16:51,420 --> 00:16:52,880
Pull yourself together, Oh Jang Mi.

290
00:16:53,750 --> 00:16:55,120
Where in the world am I?

291
00:16:58,990 --> 00:17:00,120
This place...

292
00:17:00,960 --> 00:17:02,390
I'm inside a shipping container.

293
00:17:02,660 --> 00:17:03,960
And tell Kang Baek Ho...

294
00:17:04,230 --> 00:17:05,760
to prepare an untraceable car...

295
00:17:06,160 --> 00:17:08,930
so we can leave the country
tomorrow morning.

296
00:17:09,000 --> 00:17:12,040
If I get even a whiff of the police,
or if you try any tricks,

297
00:17:12,800 --> 00:17:15,340
I can't guarantee Oh Jang Mi's life.

298
00:17:16,140 --> 00:17:19,380
Jun Ho. You have to be the go-between.

299
00:17:19,810 --> 00:17:20,940
Tonight,

300
00:17:21,380 --> 00:17:24,150
I want you to bring the money
to the meeting spot yourself.

301
00:17:25,080 --> 00:17:27,250
Oh Jang Mi's life is in your hands.

302
00:17:27,820 --> 00:17:30,820
I'm in a shipping container, Jun Ho.
An unlicensed one...

303
00:17:30,890 --> 00:17:33,920
You can't get caught,
so keep this an absolute secret. Got it?

304
00:17:36,390 --> 00:17:39,930
How dare you run your mouth?
Hey, Oh Jang Mi.

305
00:17:40,100 --> 00:17:44,000
- Are you trying to get yourself killed?
- You're not going anywhere.

306
00:17:44,500 --> 00:17:46,100
You have to pay for all your sins
until you die.

307
00:17:46,100 --> 00:17:47,200
How dare you try to flee?

308
00:17:48,670 --> 00:17:50,840
You've got some nerve,
running your mouth like that.

309
00:17:51,340 --> 00:17:55,280
Then again, you won't have much time left
to run that mouth of yours.

310
00:17:55,650 --> 00:17:58,650
Tonight, your mouth'll be shut for good.

311
00:17:59,050 --> 00:18:01,590
- What did you say?
- You think I'd leave you behind?

312
00:18:02,450 --> 00:18:05,020
At first, I only needed one of you,
not both.

313
00:18:05,390 --> 00:18:07,320
But now, I don't even need one of you.

314
00:18:07,830 --> 00:18:12,130
Oh Jang Mi. Remember this.
Today will be your last.

315
00:18:18,800 --> 00:18:21,740
Baek Ho.
We have to stay calm, especially now.

316
00:18:22,240 --> 00:18:23,740
That's the only way we'll find a solution.

317
00:18:24,640 --> 00:18:26,310
These vicious monsters...

318
00:18:26,740 --> 00:18:28,350
are making me lose my mind.

319
00:18:30,510 --> 00:18:31,920
I can't let anything happen...

320
00:18:32,580 --> 00:18:33,950
to Jang Mi.

321
00:18:34,320 --> 00:18:35,390
Nothing will happen to her.

322
00:18:35,990 --> 00:18:37,020
I'll go.

323
00:18:37,550 --> 00:18:39,590
You think they'll just let her go
if you give them the money?

324
00:18:39,920 --> 00:18:41,190
I have to be the one to go.

325
00:18:42,430 --> 00:18:45,160
What's wrong with you two? Get a grip.

326
00:18:45,460 --> 00:18:46,500
Wait.

327
00:18:47,400 --> 00:18:49,000
The photo of Jang Mi they sent you...

328
00:18:49,370 --> 00:18:50,830
I think they sent the original file.

329
00:18:51,030 --> 00:18:54,070
Right. Even on a burner phone,
when you take a picture,

330
00:18:54,370 --> 00:18:58,640
the file has the GPS latitude
and longitude coordinates embedded in it.

331
00:18:58,940 --> 00:19:00,210
Then we can find her location.

332
00:19:00,280 --> 00:19:01,980
If Lee Kang Hyuk was in such a hurry
that he sent it...

333
00:19:01,980 --> 00:19:04,080
without erasing the location data,

334
00:19:04,480 --> 00:19:06,520
we can pinpoint the location
of the shipping container...

335
00:19:06,580 --> 00:19:07,780
where Chae Hwa Young is hiding.

336
00:19:07,850 --> 00:19:09,820
Yes, we need to move fast.

337
00:19:09,820 --> 00:19:11,890
The longer we wait,
the more danger Jang Mi is in.

338
00:19:22,030 --> 00:19:24,870
How is the Chairman doing?

339
00:19:26,070 --> 00:19:28,510
He was only just discharged
from the hospital,

340
00:19:29,070 --> 00:19:30,410
and now he has to hear this.

341
00:19:30,540 --> 00:19:33,410
He got so worked up, saying he was
going to kill Chae Hwa Young,

342
00:19:34,040 --> 00:19:35,610
that he almost collapsed again.

343
00:19:36,050 --> 00:19:39,020
Is there any news about our Jang Mi?

344
00:19:40,550 --> 00:19:41,550
Yes.

345
00:19:42,120 --> 00:19:45,420
That's why I came to inform you both
and ask for your cooperation.

346
00:19:47,520 --> 00:19:50,090
Where is our Jang Mi?

347
00:19:50,230 --> 00:19:52,400
We have to find her. We must.

348
00:19:53,160 --> 00:19:54,160
We will.

349
00:20:15,890 --> 00:20:18,020
No problems with the meeting spot
for Jun Ho, right?

350
00:20:18,460 --> 00:20:20,860
We can't have that brat
betraying us again,

351
00:20:20,860 --> 00:20:22,490
so you go there ahead of time and wait.

352
00:20:22,860 --> 00:20:24,930
Got it. What should I do with Oh Jang Mi?

353
00:20:25,660 --> 00:20:27,730
- Let's just let her go.
- Are you crazy?

354
00:20:27,730 --> 00:20:29,800
I'm going through all
this torment because of Oh Jang Mi.

355
00:20:30,100 --> 00:20:33,170
I'll kill that brat
as soon as we get our hands on the money.

356
00:20:33,640 --> 00:20:38,380
No, I can't die here. Baek Ho, please.

357
00:20:44,620 --> 00:20:47,450
Look at this brat.
She can sleep in a place like this?

358
00:20:50,550 --> 00:20:51,560
Let go of me.

359
00:20:51,860 --> 00:20:54,220
So you were pretending to be asleep.
You cunning little fox.

360
00:20:55,290 --> 00:20:58,400
So this is how you seduced my Jun Ho
and made him suffer.

361
00:21:00,930 --> 00:21:02,130
It's all your fault.

362
00:21:02,430 --> 00:21:04,030
Because of you and Jung Suk Hee,

363
00:21:04,170 --> 00:21:06,570
I'm going through
all this unnecessary trouble.

364
00:21:06,640 --> 00:21:08,370
You're reaping what you sow,
Chae Hwa Young.

365
00:21:08,370 --> 00:21:10,540
Who can you blame
after living such a wicked life?

366
00:21:11,310 --> 00:21:13,440
Now, all the evil deeds you've committed

367
00:21:13,440 --> 00:21:15,380
will come back to you like a boomerang.
I guarantee it.

368
00:21:15,750 --> 00:21:19,180
Either to you,
or to the child you cherish most.

369
00:21:19,320 --> 00:21:21,350
One day, you'll pay for your wickedness,

370
00:21:21,350 --> 00:21:23,290
and you'll be crying tears of blood,
Chae Hwa Young.

371
00:21:23,350 --> 00:21:24,860
How dare you curse me!

372
00:21:25,320 --> 00:21:26,320
Hwa Young.

373
00:21:27,720 --> 00:21:28,990
Jun Ho is nearby.

374
00:21:33,430 --> 00:21:37,030
Really? The cyber team pulled
the coordinates from the metadata?

375
00:21:37,300 --> 00:21:40,670
It's the JJ Container complex
at a junkyard on the outskirts of Yongin.

376
00:21:40,940 --> 00:21:43,970
Jun Ho and I are already here.
We're counting on you.

377
00:21:44,270 --> 00:21:45,280
Okay.

378
00:21:48,010 --> 00:21:49,550
We have the location,

379
00:21:49,550 --> 00:21:51,980
but I'm worried Jang Mi will be in danger
if we bring the police.

380
00:21:52,080 --> 00:21:54,050
So only Jun Ho and Baek Ho went.

381
00:21:54,250 --> 00:21:55,620
I'll send my bodyguards as well.

382
00:21:55,690 --> 00:21:57,990
What? No, Dong Seok.

383
00:21:58,060 --> 00:22:01,120
What if our Jang Mi gets hurt?

384
00:22:01,320 --> 00:22:03,430
Don't worry,
we'll do it as safely as possible.

385
00:22:04,730 --> 00:22:06,330
We have to save our Jang Mi.

386
00:22:07,500 --> 00:22:08,500
Jang Mi.

387
00:22:18,680 --> 00:22:19,840
You came alone, right?

388
00:22:20,510 --> 00:22:21,510
Jun Ho.

389
00:22:21,680 --> 00:22:24,750
Lee Kang Hyuk, check the area
and make sure you weren't followed.

390
00:22:25,650 --> 00:22:26,650
Right.

391
00:22:29,820 --> 00:22:32,960
Kang Jun Ho. How could you report
your own mother and father?

392
00:22:34,520 --> 00:22:38,530
- You didn't do that again, did you?
- I came alone.

393
00:22:39,060 --> 00:22:42,070
You threatened Jang Mi.
How could I go to the police?

394
00:22:43,470 --> 00:22:44,470
Good.

395
00:22:55,450 --> 00:22:56,650
What do I do?

396
00:22:57,410 --> 00:22:59,020
He went to get the money.

397
00:22:59,520 --> 00:23:01,890
Am I just going to die
at the hands of Chae Hwa Young now?

398
00:23:03,250 --> 00:23:04,250
Please.

399
00:23:08,560 --> 00:23:10,560
- Jang Mi.
- Baek Ho.

400
00:23:11,430 --> 00:23:12,960
- Hang on.
- Baek Ho.

401
00:23:19,700 --> 00:23:22,210
- Baek Ho.
- Are you okay?

402
00:23:23,270 --> 00:23:26,210
- Baek Ho...
- I'm so glad you're okay.

403
00:23:26,780 --> 00:23:29,280
I was so worried
something had happened to you.

404
00:23:35,820 --> 00:23:37,920
We need to get out of here first.

405
00:23:38,760 --> 00:23:39,790
Come on.

406
00:24:08,820 --> 00:24:10,950
What do you even think of me?

407
00:24:11,690 --> 00:24:13,060
Do you even love me at all?

408
00:24:13,320 --> 00:24:16,090
What did you say?
How can you even say that?

409
00:24:16,990 --> 00:24:21,700
The person I love most in this world
is you, my son, Kang Jun Ho.

410
00:24:21,970 --> 00:24:23,670
Someone who claims to love me that much...

411
00:24:24,600 --> 00:24:25,940
turns me into a criminal?

412
00:24:26,840 --> 00:24:29,810
Because of you,
I'll be branded as a criminal...

413
00:24:30,770 --> 00:24:32,510
for the rest of my life.

414
00:24:33,240 --> 00:24:35,480
Is that how a parent shows
their love for their child?

415
00:24:35,950 --> 00:24:39,220
Yes. You have every right to resent me.

416
00:24:40,050 --> 00:24:42,090
But I had no other choice.

417
00:24:42,850 --> 00:24:43,920
Jun Ho.

418
00:24:44,820 --> 00:24:46,890
Can't you try to understand me?

419
00:24:52,860 --> 00:24:53,860
Jun Ho.

420
00:24:54,430 --> 00:24:55,730
Where's the unregistered car?

421
00:24:56,070 --> 00:24:58,970
- What about the route to get out of here?
- If you want to know, bring Jang Mi.

422
00:24:59,400 --> 00:25:01,070
What was that?

423
00:25:01,140 --> 00:25:02,270
Did you...

424
00:25:05,740 --> 00:25:06,740
What's this?

425
00:25:08,210 --> 00:25:09,350
What is this?

426
00:25:10,050 --> 00:25:13,020
- That's all the money I have.
- Kang Jun Ho. You!

427
00:25:13,950 --> 00:25:16,120
Get Oh Jang Mi. Hurry.

428
00:25:16,920 --> 00:25:19,790
No, don't go.
I told you not to hurt Jang Mi.

429
00:25:20,190 --> 00:25:21,190
Darn it.

430
00:25:28,130 --> 00:25:29,730
Jang Mi, get in the car.

431
00:25:31,700 --> 00:25:33,900
Hey. Get out of the way!

432
00:25:39,440 --> 00:25:40,880
You punk.

433
00:25:42,980 --> 00:25:44,510
(Sun Delivery)

434
00:25:46,180 --> 00:25:48,320
(Sun Delivery)

435
00:26:55,550 --> 00:26:57,550
(Subtitles are provided by KOCOWA.)
